'''''Where Stone and Wind Stood Still''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[Amphoreus]] in the chapter [[Amphoreus Annals]].

==Steps==
# Speak with "Dux Carminum" Verginia
# Hand the letter to Apollonius on Verginia's behalf
# Keep looking for Apollonius and pass the letter to him
# Speak with Verginia and the others
# Enter the ancient ruins under the city and look for Apollonius's tracks
# Head to the Janus' Maze and look for traces of Apollonius
# View the records of Apollonius using the Janus' Maze
# Learn about the guidance Apollonius received from the Janus' Maze
# Head to the entrance of Styxia and stop Apollonius, who is trying to leave the city
# Return to where Verginia is
# Reunite with Apollonius, who had returned to the feast, as well as with everyone else
# Speak with Hysilens, who is standing apart from the crowd
# Head to the entrance of Styxia and learn about Verginia's resolve
# Speak with "Dux Carminum" Verginia

